---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Tidyflow — we create clean, minimal Notion templates and digital tools to help you get organized.">

  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>About Tidyflow</h1>
    <p>Clean digital tools designed with one principle: simplicity.</p>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="post-content">
        <p>We believe getting organized shouldn't be complicated.</p>

        <p>Tidyflow creates clean, minimal digital tools — starting with Notion templates — that help you take control of your time, money, and goals. Every product is designed with one principle in mind: <strong>just open and start using</strong>.</p>

        <p>No complicated formulas. No overwhelming features. No 50-page setup guides. Just simple tools that work.</p>

        <h2>What We Make</h2>
        <p>We focus on Notion templates and Excel spreadsheets for personal productivity: budget trackers, habit trackers, project managers, and more. Each template comes with sample data so you can see exactly how it works before customizing it for yourself.</p>

        <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
        <p>The best system is the one you actually use. That's why we obsess over simplicity. If a template needs a tutorial to understand, it's too complicated.</p>

        <p>We design every product to be:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Instantly usable</strong> — duplicate and start in under 2 minutes</li>
          <li><strong>Beautifully minimal</strong> — no visual clutter, just clean layouts</li>
          <li><strong>Practically helpful</strong> — solves a real problem you have today</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="cta-box">
          <h3>Browse Our Templates</h3>
          <p>Find the right tool to help you get organized.</p>
          <a href="/products" class="cta-button">View Products →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
